title: Christopher's Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Bakery, Middle Eastern
description: A local home-style vegetarian cafe with a good vibe and energy. Has several vegan options. Offers daily morning and lunch specials, drink specials during Happy Hour from 6pm-9pm, as well as freshly baked pastries and desserts.
